## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the subjective nature of some sources, particularly user-generated content. Additionally, the complexity of media effects means that not all nuances can be captured in a single report. Further research, including empirical studies, would provide a more detailed understanding of media's impact on society.